ater","oil, for frying"]},{"title":"Prawn filling","content":["1 garlic clove","3 spring onions\/shallots, trimmed and cut into quarters","1 tbsp sesame oil","60 g water","100 g fresh shiitake mushrooms, cut into thin slices (approx. 5 mm)","250 g raw peeled prawns (approx. 24 prawns)","1 pinch salt","1 pinch ground black pepper","100 g bean sprouts","6 sprigs fresh coriander, leaves only, for garnishing"]}],"id":"r104685","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-hsJEZnfRSGw\/XZVRFq0-3qI\/AAAAAAAAdJw\/2bzTWobdFl8vG6mrjZxEFkFxiTmGIx7wQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_ejfeUIUoXAbAxcpf.png","title":"Prawn and mushroom crepes","publishedAt":"2016-05-15T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"10.9 g","fat":"9.2 g","uom":"per 1 portions","carbohydrates":"13.9 g","calories":"779 kJ \/ 185 kcal"},"usefulItems":"small bowl , large jug, fish slice, frying pan (20cm), kitchen towel, serving plates, refrigerator, stove top","basicInfo":["easy","50m","50m","8 portions"]}